            <section class="introduction">
                <h2>Shaken to the Core: Exploring Earthquakes in Seria</h2>
                <p>Seria, a town in Brunei, has experienced its fair share of seismic activity, being located in a region prone to earthquakes. These natural phenomena, driven by tectonic forces beneath the Earth's surface, have the potential to cause widespread destruction and pose significant risks to the safety and well-being of Seria's residents. In this blog post, we will delve into the topic of earthquakes in Seria, examining their causes, impacts, and the importance of preparedness in mitigating their effects.</p>
            </section>
            
            <figure>
