            <section class="introduction">
                <h2>Conclusion:</h2>
                <p>Earthquakes in Seria serve as potent reminders of the Earth's dynamic nature and the risks associated with living in seismically active regions. By understanding the causes and impacts of earthquakes, Seria can take proactive steps to enhance preparedness, strengthen infrastructure, and develop effective response and recovery strategies. Through a combination of public awareness, investment in seismic-resistant infrastructure, and community collaboration, Seria can strive towards a safer and more resilient future in the face of seismic events.</p>
